params.user: The address of the user to check

getRoleAdmin(bytes32).details: Returns the admin role that controls `role`. See {grantRole} and {revokeRole}. To change a role's admin, use {_setRoleAdmin}.

grantRole(bytes32,address).details: Grants `role` to `account`. If `account` had not been already granted `role`, emits a {RoleGranted} event. Requirements: - the caller must have ``role``'s admin role. May emit a {RoleGranted} event.

params.user: The address of the user that will lose the badge

renounceRole(bytes32,address).details: Revokes `role` from the calling account. Roles are often managed via {grantRole} and {revokeRole}: this function's purpose is to provide a mechanism for accounts to lose their privileges if they are compromised (such as when a trusted device is misplaced). If the calling account had been revoked `role`, emits a {RoleRevoked} event. Requirements: - the caller must be `callerConfirmation`. May emit a {RoleRevoked} event.

revokeRole(bytes32,address).details: Revokes `role` from `account`. If `account` had been granted `role`, emits a {RoleRevoked} event. Requirements: - the caller must have ``role``'s admin role. May emit a {RoleRevoked} event.

params.to: The address of the user that will receive the badge

params.shopAddress: The address of the shop contract

CONTROL_ROLE().notice: The Control role ID for the AccessControl contract. At first it's the msg.sender and then the shop.

approve(address,uint256).notice: Powerseller NFTs cannot be transferred, so this function is overriden to revert

nextTokenId().notice: The next tokenId to be minted

removePowersellerNFT(address).notice: Removes the PowerSeller badge from a user

safeMint(address).notice: Mints a PowerSeller badge for the user

safeTransferFrom(address,address,uint256.notice: Powerseller NFTs cannot be transferred, so this function is overriden to revert

setApprovalForAll(address,bool).notice: Powerseller NFTs cannot be transferred, so this function is overriden to revert

setShop(address).notice: Sets the shop address as the new Control role

tokenIds(address).notice: Mapping from user address to tokenId

totalPowersellers().notice: Returns the total number of users that received a PowerSeller badge

transferFrom(address,address,uint256).notice: Powerseller NFTs cannot be transferred, so this function is overriden to revert
